    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-08-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-08-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="349"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d349">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Roosevelt Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Prime
                        Minister <persName type="to">Churchill</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d349fn1">Sent to the White House Map Room, Washington, and
                        forwarded to the United States Naval Attaché, London, via Navy
                        channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Birch Island, Ontario</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-08-03">3 August
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>To the <gloss target="#t_FNP1">Former Naval Person</gloss> from the President,
                    secret and personal, Number 343.</p>
                <pb facs="0778" n="664" xml:id="pg_664"/>
                <p>Referring to your numbers 399<note n="2" xml:id="d349fn2">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_661">p. 661</ref>.</note> and
                        400,<note n="3" xml:id="d349fn3">
                        <hi rend="italic">Supra</hi>.</note> I earnestly hope that nothing will be
                    done in the matter of recognition of the Committee of National Liberation until
                    we have an opportunity to talk it over together.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
